* Running

    The run scripts take a list of Lua files as parameters.  Each file
    is executed in turn.  Here, Asteroids is used as an example

    To run Asteroids under Linux or OS X:

        $ ./electro -f examples/asteroids/asteroids.lua

    To run Asteroids under Windows, drag and drop the asteroids.lua icon
    onto the electro.bat file, or:

        C:\> electro.exe -f examples\asteroids\asteroids.lua


* Usage

        ESC - Exit
        F1  - Toggle server console
        F2  - Toggle server rendering
        F3  - Decrease server window resolution
        F4  - Increase server window resolution
        F5  - Toggle server fullscreen


